    "summary": "The user describes symptoms of a potential eye infection (redness, pain, discharge) and seeks advice on self-treatment with over-the-counter drops or old medication. The assistant correctly identifies that the symptoms suggest an infection rather than dry eyes, advises that prescription antibiotics are necessary, and repeatedly recommends seeking professional medical attention.",
